    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Bloodrager - Bloodline</strong><br/><br/><p>In the shadowy land of Nidal, the influence of Zon-Kuthon and the Midnight Lord's favored servants-the kytons- taints the land and its inhabitants. Just as an eclipse drives animals wild, so too does the darkness unleash a madness from deep within you.</p><p><b>Bonus Feats: </b>Alertness, Blind-Fight, Exotic Weapon Proficiency (spiked chain), Great Fortitude, Improved Dirty Trick, Iron Will, Toughness.</p><p><b>Bonus Spells: </b>persuasive goad (7th), pain strike (10th), deeper darkness (13th), fear (16th)</p><p><b>Bloodline Powers: </b>The sadistic power of the kytons flows through you, twisting you into a creature of pain and darkness when you bloodrage.</p>",
